<div class="section10a">
          <p>Nearly 30 years ago, Wellons began offering lumber dry kilns to complement its growing wood-fired  boiler business. The philosophy then, as it is today, was to provide customers with a modern, high-quality lumber drying system that meets their specific requirements.</p>
